Channel
          In DSM2 a channel is an entity representing a stream with a in stream length Channel.getLength(), roughness coefficient (mannings n) Channel.getMannings(), dispersion factor Channel.getDispersion() for water quality constituents It is defined by an id Channel.getId() and its two end nodes, up node Channel.getUpNodeId() and down node Channel.getDownNodeId().
